<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٧٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6272">مُعَلًّى: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6858">وُهَيْبٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6437">مُوسَى بْنِ عُقْبَةَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَتْنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/804">ابْنَةُ خَالِدِ بْنِ سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْعَاصِ </a>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّهَا سَمِعَتِ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> وَهُوَ يَتَعَوَّذُ مِنْ عَذَابِ الْقَبْرِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>